{{WealthyBarberTOC}}
----
In this chapter Roy covers The Ten Percent Solution.  Invest ten percent of all your earnings for a long-time growth.  Roy recommended that his pupils invest their ten percent into real estate and/or mutual funds. Roy (The Barber) also talks about how compound interest will make them much wealthier than they thought. example( invest $2,400 a year for 30 years at and average rate of 12 percent this would equal out to $616,000) the wonders of compound interest.

