====Python====
Python code using mpmath library<ref>[http://code.google.com/p/mpmath/ mpmath Python library]</ref>

<source lang=python>
def mandelbrot(z):
    c = z
    for i in xrange(ITERATIONS):
        zprev = z
        z = z*z + c
        if abs(z) > ESCAPE_RADIUS:
            return ctx.exp(1j*(i + 1 - ctx.log(ctx.log(abs(z)))/ctx.log(2)))
    return 0


</source>

