==Mini Mandelbrot sets==
" a saddle-node (parabolic) periodic point in a complex dynamical system often admits homoclinic points, and in the case that these homoclinic points are nondegenerate, this is accompanied by the existence of infinitely many baby Mandelbrot sets converging to the saddle-node parameter value in the corresponding parameter plane." Devaney <ref>Devaney  In Global Analysis of Dynamical Systems, ed.: H. Broer, B. Krauskopf, G. Vegter. IOP Publishing (2001), 329-338 or [http://math.bu.edu/people/bob/papers/takens.pdf Homoclinic Points in Complex Dynamical Systems]</ref>
