* DEM/M
* Boundary scanning method (BSM) : detecting the edges after Boolean escape time <ref>[http://mrob.com/pub/muency/boundaryscanning.html Boundary Scanning by Robert P. Munafo, 1993 Feb 3. ]</ref>
* boundary tracing method <ref>[http://www.ibiblio.org/e-notes/MSet/TheAlmondBreadHomepage.htm The Almond Bread Homepage]</ref><ref>[http://www.math.ucla.edu/~wittman/hyper/boundarytrackingamrxfinal.pdf Efficient Boundary Tracking Through Sampling by Alex Chen , Todd Wittman , Alexander Tartakovsky , and Andrea Bertozzi]</ref>
* contour integration by Robert Davies<ref>http://www.robertnz.net/cx.htm contour integration by Robert Davies </ref>
